sentences: Asanovic was born on 14 May 1945, in Podgorica (Montenegro).
He has received over 100 "Golden Lira", "December awards liberation Podgorica", "Oktoih-a", "Legion of Honor" medal "Knight of literature and the arts" and others.
In April 2013 he performed several pieces at the Podgorica Spring Time Chamber Music Festival, celebrating the 20th anniversary of the Andre Navarra Music School.
